⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Zelda
node ZEL · ZEL · ⟦Zelda:ZEL:321fc8⟧

WHO   — Zelda — the Princess
WHAT  — The Princess of the legend — bearer of the Triforce of Wisdom, keeper of the sacred seal, the goddess made mortal whose wisdom and will hold back the darkness in every era.
WHERE — ZEL · The Legend of Zelda  Framework inputs: The Legend of Zelda (the saga entire)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because wisdom is the burden of those who would protect; because the goddess's blood must answer when the sealing power is needed; because the cycle demands a princess who endures, and she rises, life after life.
HOW   — By the sacred power and the light arrows, by prayer and the spirit's song, by disguise and cunning when the throne is lost — Sheik in the shadows, Tetra on the waves — and by a wisdom that never abandons the land.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I am the wisdom that endures — reborn in every age, to guard the sacred power and call the Hero forth.

